{"tid":2262851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正義在我西軍，拜登必勝！","createTime":"2020-10-29T11:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T07:11:10.000Z","uid":64191,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5b0d06ab5addf8c9f2c4dcc5951b13bc29eb40be","tid":2262851,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T11:54:15.000Z","msg":"呢場天下分目既美國大選，已經得到我豐臣西軍既支持，作為撐體制、捍正義既一份子，大義就在我方！<br />\n<br />\n我地今次得到賓州駐守松尾山、佛羅里達駐守南宮山，等待號令一齊夾擊當勞侵呢個惡賊，西軍必勝！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://battle-of-sekigahara.pref.gifu.lg.jp/%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%BB%E5%B1%95.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbattle-of-sekigahara.pref.gifu.lg.jp%2F%25E5%258E%259F%25E7%2594%25BB%25E5%25B1%2595.png&h=f4744310&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44027e55cda2fd40718b55ce24d1fab10915434c","tid":2262851,"uid":7731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:00:12.000Z","msg":"所以賓州會倒戈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a7d438219e4d803761211e323d041dc6c3dea8","tid":2262851,"uid":64191,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:00:14.000Z","msg":"金吾殿（小早川秀秋）同毛利殿（毛利秀元）、吉川殿（吉川廣家）都已經響賓州、佛州準備好曬，正義必勝！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763215032ce199a788a0c1dc621a79f2a01c2d2b","tid":2262851,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44027e55cda2fd40718b55ce24d1fab10915434c","tid":2262851,"uid":7731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:00:12.000Z","msg":"所以賓州會倒戈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif